00:20:39,720 --> 00:20:41,480
Xie Wuqiang's wife, Wu Ping, claims

290
00:20:41,480 --> 00:20:42,750
she was the killer.

291
00:20:43,110 --> 00:20:45,030
Do you believe she did it?

292
00:20:48,150 --> 00:20:49,400
Do you know how far

293
00:20:49,400 --> 00:20:51,530
the crime scene is from Wu Ping's home?

294
00:20:52,880 --> 00:20:53,920
Let me tell you.

295
00:20:55,440 --> 00:20:57,240
Xie Wuqiang didn't die

296
00:20:58,160 --> 00:20:59,960
from the hammer in his left hand,

297
00:21:01,200 --> 00:21:04,200
but from a precisely
measured dose of adrenaline.

298
00:21:21,720 --> 00:21:23,120
Look at these two people.

299
00:21:23,790 --> 00:21:25,590
Yang Youmo and Xie Wuqiang.

300
00:21:26,110 --> 00:21:27,770
I'm telling you clearly.

301
00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:29,270
The same killer

302
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:32,310
murdered them both,

303
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:35,510
as well as Xiao Dade.

304
00:21:37,030 --> 00:21:38,240
Who is the killer?

305
00:21:54,880 --> 00:21:56,340
What are you trying to say?

306
00:21:56,540 --> 00:21:58,000
I need to use the bathroom.

307
00:22:03,750 --> 00:22:06,030
Dr. Liao, it's a misunderstanding.

308
00:22:06,090 --> 00:22:07,550
Thanks for your patience.

309
00:22:09,030 --> 00:22:10,030
This way, please.

310
00:22:19,220 --> 00:22:20,560
What are you doing?

311
00:22:21,510 --> 00:22:23,710
Testing whether the machine's broken.

312
00:22:29,400 --> 00:22:30,660
Ask me some questions.

313
00:22:32,590 --> 00:22:33,510
Do you

314
00:22:34,270 --> 00:22:36,110
just not like me or something?

315
00:22:38,310 --> 00:22:39,000
No.

316
00:22:42,030 --> 00:22:42,880
Lie.

317
00:22:45,240 --> 00:22:46,550
So the machine's fine.

318
00:22:46,550 --> 00:22:48,280
It's your brain that's broken.

319
00:22:48,790 --> 00:22:49,350
Did you know

320
00:22:49,350 --> 00:22:50,680
a witness came forward?

321
00:22:51,310 --> 00:22:52,350
Xiao Dade's neighbor said

322
00:22:52,350 --> 00:22:53,750
they saw the suspect.

323
00:22:54,070 --> 00:22:56,590
That person's build doesn't
match Liao Boyan at all.

324
00:22:56,590 --> 00:22:57,160
Very fat.

325
00:22:57,640 --> 00:22:58,440
Very fat?

326
00:23:04,240 --> 00:23:04,830
Chief.

327
00:23:05,200 --> 00:23:05,920
Captain Zheng.

328
00:23:05,920 --> 00:23:06,480
It's out.

329
00:23:09,160 --> 00:23:10,510
The forensic team extracted

330
00:23:10,510 --> 00:23:11,510
skin tissue from Xiao Dade's mouth.

331
00:23:11,510 --> 00:23:12,110
[Analysis result: Biological
information in Xiao Dade's blood

332
00:23:12,110 --> 00:23:12,920
Biological info

333
00:23:12,920 --> 00:23:13,010
doesn't match Liao Boyan at all.

334
00:23:13,010 --> 00:23:14,510
does not match
Liao Boyan's genetic sequence]

335
00:23:16,880 --> 00:23:17,920
Dr. Liao says

336
00:23:18,030 --> 00:23:20,720
you've been harassing him lately.

337
00:23:21,310 --> 00:23:22,040
Is that true?

338
00:23:22,330 --> 00:23:23,730
Master, I'm telling you,

339
00:23:23,830 --> 00:23:26,460
some people are just lightning rods.

340
00:23:26,510 --> 00:23:28,640
If you don't want trouble, stay away.

341
00:23:30,720 --> 00:23:33,720
Unless you go back to the force
and help Zheng Gang out.

342
00:23:34,310 --> 00:23:35,240
Not happening.

343
00:23:38,790 --> 00:23:40,450
This thing works pretty well.

344
00:24:19,510 --> 00:24:21,480
Zhi, hold it tight.

345
00:25:08,030 --> 00:25:15,150
[Jinbai Taxi]

346
00:25:27,790 --> 00:25:30,510
You get hit by lightning, why drag me

347
00:25:30,680 --> 00:25:31,590
into it?

348
00:25:32,110 --> 00:25:34,080
Might as well date you.

349
00:25:34,110 --> 00:25:36,400
That way if lightning
strikes, we get struck together.

350
00:25:36,400 --> 00:25:37,730
Why are you spacing out?

351
00:25:37,790 --> 00:25:39,300
Don't you want to follow Dr. Liao?

352
00:25:39,300 --> 00:25:41,030
Go, or you'll lose sight of him.

353
00:25:51,970 --> 00:25:55,250
[Jinbai Taxi]

354
00:26:40,110 --> 00:26:41,510
He came to see Liao Yifan.

355
00:27:11,460 --> 00:27:12,920
Did he forget where it was?

356
00:27:14,310 --> 00:27:16,440
I'm heading to the management office.

357
00:27:40,110 --> 00:27:41,270
Are you the manager here?

358
00:27:41,270 --> 00:27:41,790
Yes.

359
00:27:45,440 --> 00:27:46,700
We're with the police.

360
00:27:46,990 --> 00:27:49,050
Can you take us to Liao Yifan's grave?

361
00:28:15,720 --> 00:28:17,350
Why are you always following me?

362
00:28:17,350 --> 00:28:18,350
What do you want?

363
00:28:18,370 --> 00:28:19,650
Go away.

364
00:28:19,960 --> 00:28:20,920
Go away.

365
00:28:28,730 --> 00:28:29,920
Dr. Liao.

366
00:28:30,200 --> 00:28:31,250
Calm down.

367
00:28:32,350 --> 00:28:33,510
I'm sorry. My fault.

368
00:28:37,120 --> 00:28:38,690
I forgot.

369
00:28:40,480 --> 00:28:42,590
I forgot where

370
00:28:42,940 --> 00:28:45,460
my daughter is buried.

371
00:28:50,710 --> 00:28:54,290
I forgot where my daughter is.

372
00:28:56,830 --> 00:28:58,930
Yifan.

373
00:29:03,360 --> 00:29:03,920
Dr. Liao.

374
00:29:03,920 --> 00:29:06,000
Where are you?

375
00:29:07,350 --> 00:29:08,120
Dr. Liao.

376
00:29:10,270 --> 00:29:12,440
I know where Liao Yifan's grave is.

377
00:29:12,440 --> 00:29:13,570
I'll take you there.

378
00:29:23,850 --> 00:29:26,430
[Grave of beloved daughter Liao Yifan]

379
00:29:34,390 --> 00:29:36,650
The manager said he did this before, too.

380
00:29:37,670 --> 00:29:39,730
Forgot where Liao Yifan's grave was.

381
00:29:45,890 --> 00:29:46,880
[Nov. 19: 10 a.m. hospital follow-up;

382
00:29:46,880 --> 00:29:47,680
His notebook.

383
00:29:47,830 --> 00:29:49,780
11 a.m. buy water;
3 p.m. take medicine]

384
00:29:49,780 --> 00:29:51,670
[Nov. 18: 11:30 a.m. lunch; 3 p.m.
take medicine; 6 p.m. dinner]

385
00:29:51,760 --> 00:29:57,760
[Nov. 21: Visit daughter;
she likes wildflowers]

386
00:29:58,310 --> 00:29:59,850
Feel a bit guilty

387
00:29:59,920 --> 00:30:01,980
for suspecting him again, don't you?

388
00:30:12,710 --> 00:30:14,640
[Jinbai Taxi]

389
00:30:20,480 --> 00:30:21,940
You called the cab for him?

390
00:30:23,350 --> 00:30:24,750
He wouldn't ride in mine.

391
00:30:27,920 --> 00:30:28,720
What's this?

392
00:30:30,200 --> 00:30:31,920
Alzheimer's medication.

393
00:31:00,670 --> 00:31:04,060
[Travels with two bodyguards]

394
00:31:04,220 --> 00:31:06,480
[Zhao Qian – severe cleanliness obsession;
travels with two bodyguards]

395
00:31:06,700 --> 00:31:08,710
[Illegal waste dumping
wild, deserted, filthy]

396
00:31:18,560 --> 00:31:20,950
[Xie Wuqiang – addicted to gambling,
domestic abuser, cold-blooded]

397
00:31:28,290 --> 00:31:29,160
Who are you?

398
00:31:29,190 --> 00:31:30,130
Who are you?

399
00:31:30,200 --> 00:31:31,360
[Zhao Qian's residence
Jinniu Road, Lingpan]

400
00:32:01,980 --> 00:32:03,380
Think of your son.

401
00:32:05,160 --> 00:32:06,270
Leave the hammer.

402
00:32:06,290 --> 00:32:07,170
Run, now.

403
00:32:18,400 --> 00:32:19,640
What did you inject me with?

404
00:32:19,640 --> 00:32:21,450
The adrenaline you sold.

405
00:32:21,470 --> 00:32:23,660
That's how Yang Youmo died.

406
00:32:24,030 --> 00:32:25,470
Let's play a game.

407
00:32:26,310 --> 00:32:27,200
Win, you live.

408
00:32:27,200 --> 00:32:28,270
Lose, you die.

409
00:32:28,750 --> 00:32:30,830
The hospital is only 1.5 km away.

410
00:32:31,030 --> 00:32:33,400
From now until you stop breathing,

411
00:32:33,440 --> 00:32:34,830
less than ten minutes.

412
00:32:34,850 --> 00:32:36,440
The hospital is right there.

413
00:32:36,440 --> 00:32:38,550
Don't lose like Yang Youmo did.

414
00:32:53,700 --> 00:32:58,260
[Two days earlier]

415
00:32:58,340 --> 00:32:59,230
I'm truly grateful

416
00:32:59,230 --> 00:32:59,720
[Dade]

417
00:32:59,720 --> 00:33:01,760
for the support and
understanding of my fans.

418
00:33:01,760 --> 00:33:04,850
My new account has hit 100,000 followers.

419
00:33:04,960 --> 00:33:06,960
Time to drop a huge scoop.

420
00:33:07,270 --> 00:33:10,480
This scoop is shocking,

421
00:33:10,790 --> 00:33:12,160
bizarre beyond belief.

422
00:33:12,280 --> 00:33:12,380
And it points to someone big in Xinggang,

423
00:33:12,380 --> 00:33:14,920
[Dade]

424
00:33:14,920 --> 00:33:17,720
the head of
a well-known pharmaceutical company.

425
00:33:18,930 --> 00:33:19,630
That...

426
00:33:29,500 --> 00:33:32,320
[Sheng's – Hunan Snack Shop]

427
00:33:37,310 --> 00:33:38,660
Sir, the bill.

428
00:33:45,650 --> 00:33:46,850
Don't touch me.

429
00:33:47,160 --> 00:33:48,070
If anything happens to me,

430
00:33:48,070 --> 00:33:49,670
all the dirt will be exposed.

431
00:33:50,420 --> 00:33:51,890
I'm here to help you.

432
00:33:53,090 --> 00:33:53,890
Help me?

433
00:33:55,990 --> 00:33:57,330
Hand it over.

434
00:33:57,750 --> 00:33:59,920
I'll make sure it
works to your greatest benefit.

435
00:33:59,920 --> 00:34:01,170
What's your plan?

436
00:34:01,550 --> 00:34:03,680
The less you know, the safer you'll be.

437
00:34:04,940 --> 00:34:06,830
Then why should I trust you?

438
00:34:11,670 --> 00:34:13,889
This is Luo Lijuan's personal journal.

439
00:34:13,960 --> 00:34:15,989
It explains the real
reason she took her own life.

440
00:34:15,989 --> 00:34:16,070
[Now the song just
pierces my ears. The moment I hear it...]

441
00:34:16,070 --> 00:34:17,880
It all ties back to Zhao Qian.

442
00:34:18,030 --> 00:34:20,429
Give me the materials.
I'll take care of it.

443
00:34:23,620 --> 00:34:25,090
If I can find you,

444
00:34:25,460 --> 00:34:27,500
so can Zhao Qian's people.

445
00:34:27,699 --> 00:34:28,980
Be careful.

446
00:34:29,080 --> 00:34:30,190
Don't come back

447
00:34:30,210 --> 00:34:31,340
to this place again.

448
00:34:32,659 --> 00:34:33,790
Think it over.

449
00:34:33,920 --> 00:34:35,409
I'll find you again.

450
00:35:13,500 --> 00:35:14,630
Braised pork with preserved vegetables.

451
00:35:14,630 --> 00:35:15,630
Here's your food.

452
00:35:15,840 --> 00:35:16,440
Thank you.

453
00:35:16,490 --> 00:35:18,630
Sir, one stir-fried pork for me.

454
00:35:18,660 --> 00:35:19,770
Sure, find a seat.

455
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:20,880
Make it to-go.

456
00:35:21,110 --> 00:35:22,190
Okay, okay.

457
00:37:37,950 --> 00:37:43,820
[Medicine]

458
00:37:54,150 --> 00:37:55,020
Dr. Liao.

459
00:38:00,150 --> 00:38:01,370
Hello, Ms. Zhao.

460
00:38:01,590 --> 00:38:03,520
You watched my stream, didn't you?

461
00:38:04,320 --> 00:38:05,350
Xiao Dade?

462
00:38:06,000 --> 00:38:07,360
So you did see it.

463
00:38:08,670 --> 00:38:10,300
How did you get my number?

464
00:38:10,670 --> 00:38:12,790
The power of the internet is vast.

465
00:38:12,840 --> 00:38:15,100
Someone will always dig up your secrets.

466
00:38:15,360 --> 00:38:16,480
Mr. Xiao,

467
00:38:16,710 --> 00:38:18,510
we live in a lawful society now.

468
00:38:18,840 --> 00:38:20,880
Spreading rumors has serious consequences.

469
00:38:20,880 --> 00:38:23,000
You've already
learned that lesson, haven't you?

470
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:24,200
Still didn't sink in?

471
00:38:25,230 --> 00:38:27,000
But what if I have evidence?

472
00:38:27,000 --> 00:38:29,090
Would it still count as a rumor?

473
00:38:29,210 --> 00:38:29,850
Well?

474
00:38:29,870 --> 00:38:30,760
Don't you want to know

475
00:38:30,760 --> 00:38:32,510
how much my evidence is worth?

476
00:38:32,710 --> 00:38:33,480
No.

477
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:34,400
What?

478
00:38:37,110 --> 00:38:39,550
I hate being threatened.

479
00:39:00,750 --> 00:39:02,180
What are you trying to do?

480
00:39:02,440 --> 00:39:03,640
Hand it over.

481
00:39:03,800 --> 00:39:05,030
Hand over what?

482
00:39:05,760 --> 00:39:07,760
The most valuable thing you've got.

483
00:39:13,840 --> 00:39:14,870
Let go.

484
00:39:46,000 --> 00:39:47,460
I took something from you,

485
00:39:47,690 --> 00:39:49,420
now I'm giving something back.

486
00:40:11,190 --> 00:40:12,390
People die for money.

487
00:40:13,370 --> 00:40:15,320
Long, burn extra for him.

488
00:40:27,630 --> 00:40:27,750
My son is dead.

489
00:40:27,750 --> 00:40:29,630
[October 26, 2017]

490
00:40:29,630 --> 00:40:31,390
They all say it was an accident.

491
00:40:31,550 --> 00:40:32,670
But do you know?

492
00:40:33,320 --> 00:40:34,590
If not for Zhao Qian,

493
00:40:34,590 --> 00:40:37,380
that "accident" never would've happened.

494
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:40,450
I was seduced by Zhao Qian.

495
00:40:40,760 --> 00:40:42,730
If she hadn't given me that signal,

496
00:40:43,550 --> 00:40:46,270
I never would've done it.

497
00:40:46,330 --> 00:40:47,390
Did it go smoothly?

498
00:40:47,640 --> 00:40:48,330
Smoothly.

499
00:40:48,590 --> 00:40:50,050
Did you get the materials?

500
00:40:51,480 --> 00:40:52,210
No.

501
00:40:54,760 --> 00:40:57,480
Xiao Dade didn't have anything solid.

502
00:40:58,400 --> 00:41:00,400
He just wanted to blackmail you.

503
00:41:01,050 --> 00:41:02,960
Then why'd you say it went smoothly?

504
00:41:02,960 --> 00:41:03,760
Ms. Zhao.

505
00:41:04,670 --> 00:41:06,440
No evidence.

506
00:41:06,460 --> 00:41:08,720
Isn't that the smoothest result for you?

507
00:41:10,630 --> 00:41:12,160
So how did you deal with him?

508
00:41:12,970 --> 00:41:14,700
The way you taught me.

509
00:41:21,630 --> 00:41:23,630
The camera's not going to Zhao Qian?

510
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:27,690
You know

511
00:41:28,510 --> 00:41:29,710
what a dog wants most?

512
00:41:30,870 --> 00:41:31,680
A bone.

513
00:41:34,230 --> 00:41:36,030
And do you know

514
00:41:37,250 --> 00:41:39,050
how to use a bone to toy with a dog?

515
00:42:26,150 --> 00:42:27,840
Mr. Zhao, it's getting late.

516
00:42:27,840 --> 00:42:29,160
You should rest.

517
00:42:31,030 --> 00:42:31,800
Ms. Shen.

518
00:42:32,590 --> 00:42:33,550
Go rest.

519
00:42:40,110 --> 00:42:40,880
Dad,

520
00:42:43,400 --> 00:42:45,000
remember this dance tune?

521
00:42:50,190 --> 00:42:51,850
When you dance,

522
00:42:52,150 --> 00:42:53,810
you have to control the floor.

523
00:42:53,960 --> 00:42:55,330
You treat your partner

524
00:42:55,880 --> 00:42:57,480
like a puppet on strings.

525
00:42:59,030 --> 00:43:00,110
Now,

526
00:43:00,710 --> 00:43:01,960
I'm a master at that.

527
00:43:04,450 --> 00:43:05,240
Right?

528
00:43:09,710 --> 00:43:11,840
It feels so good to control people.

529
00:43:15,670 --> 00:43:16,480
Dad,

530
00:43:17,110 --> 00:43:18,970
I'm in such a great mood,

531
00:43:19,190 --> 00:43:21,170
I really want to dance with you.

532
00:43:21,710 --> 00:43:23,460
Too bad you can't stand up.

533
00:43:25,880 --> 00:43:26,880
What should we do?

534
00:43:29,440 --> 00:43:30,510
No worries.

535
00:43:31,430 --> 00:43:32,840
Even if you can't stand,

536
00:43:34,320 --> 00:43:35,740
you can still dance.

537
00:43:36,150 --> 00:43:38,610
You can feel
what it's like to be controlled.

538
00:44:24,950 --> 00:44:30,780
[The Perfect Suspect]
